window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He'll make sure she never wants to leave....&nbsp;</p> <p>Holly never thought she'd move back to her hometown, but then something terrible happened. She doesn't know if she can recover. But she knows she can never tell another soul.&nbsp;</p> <p>People say her neighbour, David, is 'different'. He doesn't go out much, and never after dark. But in David, Holly finds just what she needs: a friend. Someone who's always there.&nbsp;</p> <p>No-one knows Holly's secret or where she lives. She has left the past behind. She is sure of it. So why does she feel as though she's in terrible danger?&nbsp;</p>"; 
